subproject.description:
1. Awareness raised and knowledge shared with government delegates, civil society, and international organizations about the centrality of gender equality to effective policy and programmatic implementation
2. Capacity built at all levels to design and implement gender-responsive climate change policies, strategies and programmes in Africa and Asia and the Pacific.
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
subproject.title: Gender responsive CC policies

subproject.corporate outcome: Inclusive growth and social equity promoted through pro-poor macroeconomic and fiscal policies that support income, employment and social protection of  youth, women and vulnerable groups in a sustainable way
